      "id": "monument",
      "at": [820, 560],
      "kind": "examine",
      "label": "The Founders' Monument",
      "interactions": [
        {
          "id": "dust_library",
          "cond": { "all": [{ "day": { "gte": 2 } }, { "not": { "flag": "dust_library_done" } }] },
          "opens": "puzzle:dust_library",
          "ref": "II.13.1"
        },
        {
          "id": "wax_scrapings",
          "cond": { "all": [{ "flag": "dust_library_done" }, { "not": { "card": "wax_scrapings" } }] },
          "text": "On the vault's lip, where a careful hand would rest an envelope on the way out: flecks of green wax, scraped thin. The sealed envelope came out LAST — lifted deliberately, over everything else.",
          "effects": [{ "giveCard": "wax_scrapings", "status": "verified" }],
          "ref": "II.12.4"
        },
        {
          "id": "monument_post_ceremony",
          "cond": { "flag": "ceremony_done" },
          "text": "The vault door stands open at the monument's base. Fifty years of waiting, and inside: clean stone, old dust, and nothing at all. The bunting overhead has already begun to sag.",
          "ref": "I.5.day1"
        },
        {
          "id": "monument_pre_ceremony",
          "text": "The Founders' Monument, scrubbed for its birthday. Behind the brass vault door at its base: the time capsule, sealed fifty years ago tonight. Half the district has touched the door 'for luck' this week.",
          "ref": "I.2"
        }
      ],
      "ref": "I.2"
    },
    {
      "id": "julians_ring",
      "at": [1350, 640],
      "kind": "chekhov",
      "label": "The Heir at Work",
      "cond": { "not": { "flag": "ceremony_done" } },
      "detail": {
        "tier": "character",
        "text": "Julian Vale, shaking hands, smiling the practiced smile. Between handshakes his thumb finds his father's signet ring and spins it — around, around. Probably nothing. Gary writes it down anyway.",
        "flag": "noticed_julian_ring",
        "cond": {}
      },
      "ref": "I.5.day1"
    },
    {
      "id": "dedication_plaque",
      "at": [620, 620],
      "kind": "examine",
      "label": "The Dedication Plaque",
      "cond": { "day": { "gte": 3 } },
      "interactions": [
        {
          "id": "then_now",
          "cond": { "all": [{ "card": "founding_photograph" }, { "not": { "flag": "then_now_founding_done" } }] },
          "opens": "puzzle:then_now_founding",
          "ref": "II.13.2"
        },
        {
          "id": "plaque_after",
          "cond": { "flag": "then_now_founding_done" },
          "text": "The dedication plaque, a full stride from where the founding photograph shows it. Moved ten years ago — to make room for something added behind it.",
          "ref": "II.13.2"
        },
        {
          "id": "plaque_look",
          "text": "The founders' dedication plaque, polished for the anniversary. Something about its position itches at Gary — the kind of itch that wants an old photograph.",
          "ref": "II.13.2"
        }
      ],
      "ref": "II.13.2"
    },
    {
